  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of libxcb</title>

    <para>
      Install libxcb by running the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../libxcb-&libxcb-version;-automake_bug-1.patch &amp;&amp;
sed -e "s/pthread-stubs//" -i configure.ac &amp;&amp;
autoreconf -fi &amp;&amp;
./configure $XORG_CONFIG \
            --docdir='${datadir}'/doc/libxcb-&libxcb-version; \
            --enable-xinput \
            --enable-xkb &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    <sect3 role="commands">
      <title>Command Explanations</title>

      <para>
        <command>sed -e "s/pthread-stubs//" -i configure.ac</command>: This sed
        removes dependency on libpthread-stubs package which is useless on
        Linux.
      </para>

      <para>
        <parameter>--enable-xinput</parameter>: This switch enables XCB Xinput
        extension.
      </para>

      <para>
        <parameter>--enable-xkb</parameter>: This switch enables XCB XKB
        extension.
      </para>

    </sect3>

  </sect2>

